{"tid":555040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察通訊員假「醫生紙」呃50日假 串錯字被揭料判囚","createTime":"2018-02-09T05:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T00:11:19.000Z","uid":31314,"like":175,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"b8853128397189976d199002c95bc78194ca2d32","tid":555040,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:28:11.000Z","msg":"駐守新界北管制中心的已婚35歲警察通訊員麥國生，聲稱因長期未能適應工作壓力，製造虛假「醫生紙」，惟在2017年1月向上級呈遞的「醫生紙」中錯串英文字，惹起懷疑，上級向醫管局查詢後揭發事件。麥今在粉嶺裁判法院承認23項使用虛假文書罪，案件押後至3月2日，有待裁判官為被告索取背景報告，被告期間須還柙。<br />\n<br />\n　　練錦鴻主任裁判官指，案件涉及違反誠信，被告犯案並不是一時之快，案發時間長達兩年，故被告很大機會被判處監禁式刑罰，以向社會傳達警惕的信息，及令大眾明白此為何等讓人厭惡的行為。<br />\n<br />\n　　案情指，在2015年10月6日至17年1月21日間，被告23次製造共40張虛假「醫生紙」，騙取50天病假，涉及約3萬4千元薪水。"},{"pid":"24f1c7bee5ff6236b680c9e9243d9dbcfb0e2b0a","tid":555040,"uid":96871,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:31:29.000Z","msg":"+1分"},{"pid":"98398ec92337a64fbc05728b0258329700300ad6","tid":555040,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T06:17:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195ebd232e34ff97e49d3387225a98a8891b64c2","tid":555040,"uid":41821,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T06:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n犯罪集團"},{"pid":"03b8199bb667c3399f6fdf141c5b7c4dc8bb2283","tid":555040,"uid":46933,"like":126,"dislike":0,"score":126,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"判決好影響士氣"},{"pid":"0292acde0a7fb08efb87a4d73fa07e9af7b53582","tid":555040,"uid":32006,"like":25,"dislike":4,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T06:26:47.000Z","msg":"@ 肥絲大隻"},{"pid":"130806c46c5705e3c667672c3b7996522cc614b0","tid":555040,"uid":51127,"like":83,"dislike":2,"score":81,"quote":{"pid":"03b8199bb667c3399f6fdf141c5b7c4dc8bb2283","tid":555040,"uid":46933,"like":126,"dislike":0,"sco